The evidence with the title 'Senior scare, yet again - factcheck.org ' says Sep 8, 2009  ... The ad refers to a proposal endorsed by most House Republicans as part of the alternative budget they presented earlier this year .  ... Preserving the current Medicare program for anyone now receiving it , or within 10 years of qualifying for it .  ... It 's a plan to change Medicare significantly but not to "abolish" it. 
